Öyleyse, seni de çalacağım!!

00:02:59.740 --> 00:03:01.780
"Tanrı"
Gum-Gum...

00:03:01.780 --> 00:03:01.840
Gum-Gum...

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:05.250
